About this hotel

Set in gardens surrounded by arid countryside, this high-end hotel with views of the Atlas Mountains is 11 km from both Jemaa el-Fnaa, a bustling market square, and the ornate Koutoubia Mosque.

    About this hotel

    Set in gardens surrounded by arid countryside, this high-end hotel with views of the Atlas Mountains is 11 km from both Jemaa el-Fnaa, a bustling market square, and the ornate Koutoubia Mosque.

    Upscale rooms with Arabic motifs offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screens and DVD players, plus minibars, tea and coffeemakers, and terraces. Upgraded rooms have views of the pool or mountains. Suites feature gardens and/or private pools.

    Breakfast, parking and a city center shuttle are included. There's also a polished restaurant with garden views, plus a sports bar and a lounge bar. Other amenities consist of a gym, an outdoor pool, and a spa featuring a hammam.
